org.eclipse.papyrus.RobotML
Interface WheelSystem

All Superinterfaces:
ActuatorSystem, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, RoboticSystem, System
All Known Implementing Classes:
WheelSystemImpl
public interface WheelSystem
extends ActuatorSystem

A representation of the model object 'Wheel System'.

The following features are supported:

  • Wheel Radius
  • Wheel Width
  • Suspension Rest Length
  • Wheel Connection Height
  • Type Of Wheel
  • Wheel Velocity PI Dkp
  • Wheel Velocity PI Dki
  • Wheel Velocity PI Dkd
  • Wheel Steering PI Dkp
  • Wheel Steering PI Dkd
  • Wheel Friction
  • Suspension Stiffness
  • Suspension Damping
  • Suspension Compression
  • Wheel Velocity PI Dmax Sum
  • Wheel Velocity PI Dmax Val

See Also:
RobotMLPackage.getWheelSystem()
